name: George Panchev
description: Talking about who i’m,am that easy going type, adventurous, romantic, ambitious and have a very good sense of humor.. My hobbies are too many but to mentioned a few; sports,watching movies, going for walks, listening to music (almost all types of music), love on the beach, dancing in the dark etc. I am looking for a honest, loyal, trustworthy, fun, caring and a loving woman who is interested in a serious relationship. I want to love and be loved. I have been alone for 7 years now and i am ready to be with someone. I miss having someone special in my life.
